Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:25.81,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H242424&\fs90\pos(1310.4,450)}chin\N子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:24.81,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H242424&\fs60\frz21.84\pos(320,892.8)}請\N多\N關\N照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:25.81,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H242424&\fs60\frz21.84\pos(331.2,572.8)}請\N多\N關\N照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:29.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,與剛學會撓父母癢癢的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:32.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就算叫停也絕對不會停下一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:35.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,非常開心的藤原也絕對不會停下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:37.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:39.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:43.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:44.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:46.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了藤原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:49.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在男生面前不能說剛才的那個詞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:53.42,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs80\b1\bord5\c&HBFF3FD&\3c&H768DF0&}微\N笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:52.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有停下來的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 我也是淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:59.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不會在男生面前說那種詞的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:02.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不會從自己嘴裡說出來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:04.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 這個說法有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:07.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個那個 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:10.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有軌電車的另一個說法是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:12.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有軌電車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:14.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,叮叮車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙想讓會長說chinchin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果從會長嘴裡聽到那個詞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:23.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定 會笑出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓會長說出chinchin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:27.55,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 確實有各種說法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要擺脫這個局面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:33.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,快想 全力轉動大腦 四宮輝夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像叫chin…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:37.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Tram
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:41.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,英語應該是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:47.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,成魚叫黑鯛 幼魚的時候叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:48.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,chinc…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:51.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,babatare 關西好像就是這麼叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,意大利語乾杯怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:53.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,cin c…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:56.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,salute 原指健康的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯的時候也會說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:01.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 還有什麼還有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:05.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:06.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,防守成功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:10.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣會長就不會說chinchin這個詞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,總算逃過一劫了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:18.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1185.6,1010)}露出丁丁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:18.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我只是想讓會長說出chinchin而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:18.52,Kaguya_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,說出和露出都是「出す」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:19.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:20.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因為輝夜同學搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:23.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1121.6,1010)}露出丁丁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:23.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就不能讓會長說出chinchin了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:24.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,變態！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:26.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那東西怎麼可能在這裡露出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:28.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:34.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,女流氓嗎 你們是女流氓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:38.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:45.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:49.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,chinchin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:52.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:21:54.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,實在太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:56.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(955.2,1010)}丁丁討厭死了
